{"tid":1630800,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[不難想像]習帝唔識字搞出大頭佛","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:54:01.000Z","uid":62067,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ab838877269e7fc6627fddbada0e213be6b7f14b","tid":1630800,"uid":62067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:42:45.000Z","msg":"當初有人個初心可能真係「止暴制亂」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點知鄰近地區最大嗰隻維尼熊同黑警一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔讀書又唔識字，密函寫咗「只暴制乱」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />照字面睇即係「只用暴力，制造暴乱」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />777又只識死跟唔問敢點解，就係咁香港就死喺喱個女魔頭手上<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9221676b5af5015abeae04745714801cee51e08a","tid":1630800,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:45:39.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"af903ec7ec3529d27df66cfb16ab226cc9588f76","tid":1630800,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:45:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【政府製造經濟危機】以最和理非既方式 擊敗港共<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630641</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0ab8278b7b0672a9e2b662db790c998d7152cf","tid":1630800,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:49:04.000Z","msg":"邊個大大聲話集中<br />\n<br />\n鞭屍時間<br />\n<br />\n集中撚答到我問題，先好叫人出黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"11a94b751e31c087bc874e25c2a69e47e5c82336","tid":1630800,"uid":324984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:54:01.000Z","msg":"好好笑 ！"}]}